Company Overview
Rockmill Financial Consulting, LLC operates as a governmental financial advisor and consultant company in Ohio. The company offers services in the areas of public finance, economic development, asset management, financial communications, and budget and forecasting; and research and analysis, such as custom research of economic data, staffing issues, tax comparisons, and more. It serves state agencies, counties, cities, villages, townships, school districts, charter schools, colleges, universities, port authorities, sanitation districts, water districts, waste water districts, parks and recreation districts, special authorities, and others. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Lanc...
Rockmill Financial Consulting, LLC operates as a governmental financial advisor and consultant company in Ohio. The company offers services in the areas of public finance, economic development, asset management, financial communications, and budget and forecasting; and research and analysis, such as custom research of economic data, staffing issues, tax comparisons, and more. It serves state agencies, counties, cities, villages, townships, school districts, charter schools, colleges, universities, port authorities, sanitation districts, water districts, waste water districts, parks and recreation districts, special authorities, and others. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Lancaster, Ohio.
