        Public Finance  
        
      



HomeServices  Public Finance



Rockmill’s public finance services are designed to give our clients the peace of mind they are getting reliable guidance. The kind of guidance that will produce exceptional results. Our approach is designed to provide a clear understanding of the options that are available, and the benefits of using them. We take our time to understand the goals that are the most important to you and your community. Then we make them a reality.

Public Finance Services



Selection of Underwriters

We will:

identify potential bond underwriters
act as a liaison between you and the underwriter
create a process to select the underwriter
create a system to rank underwriting firms
recommend the best underwriter
write the job requirements for the underwriter
engage them into the financing process
explain the underwriter’s responsibilities




Determining financial structure

We will:

identify financing constraints
develop client goals
identify legal and market requirements
develop structural options for your consideration
present a deal structure that’s most attractive to you




Assist with preparing Official Statements

We will:

provide an outline of the required information
provide you a clear explanation of the material
identify the information we are capable of obtaining
collect information on your behalf
help you gather your information
review all information for accuracy and consistency
coordinate communication of data to Counsel
review the final O.S. for accuracy and consistency




Credit (Bond) rating analysis and measurement

We will:

conduct a detailed financial analysis of the client
create a matrix to identify the client’s rating potential
use the matrix to determine if a upgrade is possible
use the matrix to develop a rating “plan”
present the plan to the governing body




Credit rating preparation

We will:

use the rating plan to develop a presentation strategy
schedule practice meetings
host each meeting
identify participants needed in the presentation
develop the presentation outline
develop the presentation material
